E. Hunter Harrison - Wikipedia





















 






E. Hunter Harrison

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

Ewing Hunter Harrison (born November 7, 1944[1]) is a railway executive who served as the CEO of Illinois Central Railroad (IC), Canadian National Railway (CN) and Canadian Pacific Railway (CPR), and now serves as CEO of CSX.
Biography[edit]
